\mt1 EFESAS
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Wun Pol wun. Wunay…® lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wuta ngwuk kat kwiga. God wand…® maa Kraist jisasna nj…®vwa aposelat t…®ga kwut…®gowun. Efesas wal…®nja ngepmamba t…®ga Godna mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk kat kan pas p…®l…®wutaa kwigowun. Ngwuk Kraist Jisas kat maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa yet…®l…®gangwuk.
\v 2 N…®na nyaek Godno n…®no njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistno ngwuk kat awagapma kwunapmb…®k maa apma vat t…®ngwangat wowun.
\s1 GOD N∆óN KAT APMA VAT YIND∆ó
\p 
\v 3 Kraistna mbaapma wulein…®n maa God n…®n kat apma vat yind…®. Nyinangwutna apma nda n…®n kat aywaa kwind…®. Ngi kat t…®ga n…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistna nyaek God nd…® kat n…®ma s…®vu k…®ga t…®giyan…®n.
\v 4 Tamba God k…®pma ana kwuka l…®nd…®. kwutapman t…®ga yelav…®tnd…®. Wundi n…®mba ng…®ni Kraistna mbaapma wuleigiyandi waa yelav…®tnd…®. Wuleilaa kavle wak yilapman apma vat m…®na yiga yet…®nan kat God n…®n kat wand…®. n…®n kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka ndi kat kwutaa Kraistna mbaapmamba taagagiyowun waa yelav…®ka t…®nd…®.
\v 5 Tamba God n…®n kat yelav…®tnd…®. Jisas Kraist ndi kat kwutaa kiyand…® maa wuna nyanguat t…®giyandi waa nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®ka t…®nd…®.
\v 6 God wand…® maa nd…®na apma nyan n…®n kat kwunapmak ngaga yand…®. God n…®n kat awagapma apma vat yind…®. Nd…® kat s…®vu k…®gan…®n.
\p 
\v 7-8 Tak wan kavle vat n…®n kat ngilaa t…®nd…®. Kraist n…®n kat t…®ga kiyand…® maa ng…®ni ana wan nda ngilaa l…®gand…®. N…®na kavle vat tamba s…®l…®mbwind…®. God n…®n kat n…®ma vat awagapma apma vat yind…®. God n…®n kat apma maawut yelav…®taa n…®n kat yind…®.
\v 9 God nd…®na maawupmba yindeya vak kat yelav…®t t…®nd…®. Kraist kat wowun maa ndi kat yiga kwunak kiyand…® waa yelav…®t t…®nd…®. Tak yelav…®t…®nda vak pogwula t…®nd…®. Mbambala pogwul…®nda vak tamba n…®n kat v…®s…®mogwind…®.
\v 10 God nd…®na yelav…®tnda vak ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla God wand…® maa kak kiyaigand…®. Wan vak k…®ngiyand…®. K…®pmamba l…®ga nda nyinangwupmba l…®ga nda aywaa God ndi kat kwutaa kiyalaa yaa k…®tamba t…®ndi, Kraist ndina njambwi nyanat t…®giyand…®. God wan vak kat maawupmba yelav…®tnd…®.
\p 
\v 11 Mbambala l…®ga vak ng…®ni yaiga vat kwo ana yaigand…®. God maawupmba yelav…®taa wand…® maa yaigand…®. God tamba nglei maawupmba yelav…®aa wand…® maa mbambala Kraistna mbaapma wuleilaa nd…®nogwionana k…®tamba yet…®l…®gan…®n.
\v 12 N…®n Juda tak Kraistna nyaang…®t wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa t…®n…®n. God n…®n kat apma vat yind…®. Nd…® apma nyana waa wal…®gan…®n.
\p 
\v 13 Ngwuk Juda ana ngwuk. Ngwutno ng…®ni Kraistna apma nyaang…®t wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka ngwutno kwutaa l…®ngwuk. Kwutaa l…®ngwuk maa ngwutna kavle vat s…®l…®mwind…®. s…®l…®mbwilaa ngwuk wuna n…®mba ngwuk walaa nd…®na waagan ngwuk kat kwind…®. Wuna waagan kwigiyowun waa tak wanda vapmba ngwuk kat kwind…®. Nd…®na waagan n…®n kat kwind…®, klalaa n…®n nd…®na n…®mba n…®n waa yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n.
\v 14 God n…®n kat mbambala samat kwunatnd…®. Ng…®ni wuna n…®mba ngwuk ngwuk kat aywaa kwunakiyowun waa God n…®n kat wand…®. N…®n kat kwinda waagan klalaa woseka ana wand…®. Ng…®ni aywaa n…®n kat kwunakiyand…® waa yelav…®t…®gan…®n. God apma vat yind…®. Nd…® apma nyana waa wal…®gan…®n.
\s1 POL NDI KAT T∆óGA GOD KAT WAGALAND∆ó
\p 
\v 15 Njambwi nyan Jisas kat maawupmba yelav…®ka kwuta l…®ngwa vak wuno wukwun. Godna n…®mba kat n…®ma maawupmba yelav…®ka kwunat…®ngwa vak wuno wukwun.
\v 16 Wutaa ngwutna s…® waga God kat s…®vu k…®l…®gowun nj…®mbla nj…®mbla. God kat wagalaweya nj…®mbla ngwuk kat apma vat yil…®nda vak kat yelav…®ka t…®gowun.
\v 17 N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistna nyaek God ngwuk kat apma maawut kwindangat wagala t…®gowun. Nd…®namba apma maawut klalaa apma vak yelav…®ka Godna angwa vak v…®ga l…®giyangwuk.
\v 18 Godna angwa vak kemba l…®ga nda vla t…®gand…®. Nd…®na angwa vak ngwulo v…®ngwangat wagala t…®gowun. Nd…®na angwa vak v…®laa ng…®ni ngwuk kat yindeya apma vat mbambala v…®giyangwuk. Mbambala wan vak klavak kawiga l…®gangwuk. Ngwuk kat yindeya apma vatna sakwat mbambala v…®giyangwuk.
\v 19-20 Nd…®na angwa vak v…®laa nd…® kat kwutaa la n…®mba n…®n n…®n kat kwinda kwondu v…®giyangwuk. Tagula ava l…®ga kwondua. N…®n kat kwinda kwondu tak Kraist kat kwind…® maa kiyalaa l…®ga laatnd…®. Laataa nyinangwut wokelaa nd…®na nyaek Godna yaagindan naang…®mba ndaa l…®gand…®.
\v 21 Ndaa l…®ga njambwi nyan t…®ga nat n…®mba kat y…®ga l…®gand…®. Nyinangwupmba l…®ga njambwi l…®ga n…®ma n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®gand…®. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga njambwi n…®mba ndina n…®ma nyana. Ng…®ni t…®giyaa njambwi n…®mba ndina n…®ma nyanat t…®giyand…®.
\v 22 God wand…® maa nd…®na njambwi nyanat t…®gand…®. God wand…® maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbana njambwi nyanat t…®gand…®. Nat n…®mba kat kwulat…®ga nyan ndina njambwi nyanat t…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga nat n…®mba kat ana vaak kiyandi nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba.
\v 23 Kraistna mbaapma n…®mba nd…®na mbang…® vla l…®gandi. Nd…® ndina nambu vla t…®gand…®. Nd…®nai kwiya kwondumba nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nj…®vwa kwut…®gandi. Nyinangwut k…®pmamba l…®ga nda aywaa nd…®nai kwiya kwondumba ndina nj…®vwa kwut…®gand…®.
\c 2
\s1 KIYALAA L∆óGA LAAKNA N∆óMBA VLA T∆óGANGWUK
\p 
\v 1 Tamba ngwuk Juda ana ngwuk aywaa God kat kai waa kavle savle yiga yet…®ngwuk. Ngwuk kiya n…®mba vla yet…®ngwuk.
\v 2 Ngwuk tamba nj…®mbla k…®pmana kavle vak kwuka kavle vat yeta waagana njambwi nyana kwundimba yet…®ngwuk. Mbambala wan kavle nyan God kat kai wal…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyana.
\v 3 God kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba n…®n aywaa tamba yet…®nja vla yet…®n…®n. N…®na kavle maawut yelav…®ka n…®na mbang…®na kavle kwundi wuka yet…®n…®n. God kavle n…®mba kat s…®ndeya vak vla n…®no n…®n kat wupma s…®genda.
\p 
\v 4 N…®n kat ana s…®nd…®. N…®n kat n…®mamba miwa yiga n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®nd…®.
\v 5 N…®n tamb Godna kwundi wupmak kat kai wan…®n. Kiya n…®mba vla l…®n…®n. God wand…® maa Kraist n…®n kat kwunatnd…® maa apma vat t…®n…®n Kraist kiyalaa laatnda vla kiyaga laakna nd…®na n…®mba vla t…®gan…®n. God n…®n kat awagapma kwo kwundatnd…®. N…®mamba wengaklalaa t…®ga ana kwunatnd…®.
\v 6 Kraist Jisasna mbaapma wulein…®n maa God n…®n kat wand…®. Wuna nyannyinangwut wokelaa nat n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®nda vla ngwulo nd…®nogwinana v…®ga t…®giyangwuk waa wand…® God.
\v 7 N…®n kat manda kat wupma wand…®. N…®n kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka Jisas Kraist kat ay wand…®. Jisas Kraist yalaa n…®n kat kwunaka kalil…®nda vak v…®laa nat n…®mba waigandi. God ndi kat awagapma apma vat yind…® waa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla waigandi.
\v 8 God kat yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®n…®n maa n…®n kat God kwo kwunatnd…®. N…®n n…®na maawupmba avla ana kwunatn…®n. Godna maawupmba n…®n kat two kwunatnd…®.
\v 9 N…®n n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka n…®n avla ana kwunatn…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga k…®ta nyan wun n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka avla kwunakwun. Apma nyan wun waa ana waigqand…®. God nd…® n…®n kat kwo kwunatnd…®.
\v 10 Tamba God n…®n kat yelav…®tgnd…®. Wundi n…®mba Kraist Jisasna mbaapma wuleilaa apma nj…®vwa kwukiyandi waa God yelav…®taa nsn kat kwutnd…®.
\s1 KRAIST MBAAPMA V∆óL∆óL∆óK KWUTAA K∆óTA S∆óMBA T∆óGIYAMB∆óK WAA WAND∆ó
\p 
\v 11 Ngwuk Juda ana ngwuk. Juda ndina mbang…® p…®t…®gandi. Ngwuk kat v…®laa wal…®gandi. Mbang…® p…®tapman t…®ga n…®mba ndi waa wal…®gandi. Tamba yiga yet…®ngwa vak kat yelav…®k ngwula.
\v 12 Tamba Kraistna nyaang…®t ana wuka t…®ngwuk. Tamba Godna n…®mba vla ana t…®ngwuk. Ngwuk n…®m…®ngi vla t…®ngwuk. God Juda kat kwinda vak ngwuk ana klal…®ngwuk. Ndi kat mbuta nyaang…®t ana wuka l…®ngwuk. Ngwuk Godna nyaang…®t wutapman t…®ga kwo yet…®ngwuk. God n…®n kat ng…®ni apma vat yigiyand…® waa ana yelav…®ka yet…®ngwuk.
\v 13 Mbambala s…®vla ngepma t…®ga n…®mba vla ana t…®gangwuk. Kraist ngwuk kat t…®ga kiyalaa ngwuk kat kwutaa nd…®na mbaapmamba taagand…®. Mbambala nd…®nogwinana k…®tamba yet…®ga Judogwinala k…®ta ngepma n…®mba vla t…®gangwuk.
\v 14 Tamba Judagwi Juda ana ndi nat n…®mbo awat sowat ndi kai wal…®ndi. Ksi wal…®nja vak ndina n…®nd…®mba k…®l…®nja t…®vwi vla l…®nd…®. Nd…® Kraist ndi kat t…®ga kiyand…® maa kai wal…®nja vat ng…®l…®nd…®. T…®vwi ndanda vla ng…®l…®nd…®.
\v 15 Judana njambia t…®ga nyaang…®k kat Kraist kai waakal…®tnd…®. Juda wal…®nja n…®mbo nat n…®mbo ndi kat Kraist kwutaa nd…®na k…®ta mbaapmamba taagand…®. Taagand…® maa awat sowat kai wal…®nja vak ng…®l…®nd…®.
\v 16 Kraist ndi kat t…®ga kiwai krosmba kiyand…® maa mbapma v…®l…®l…®k n…®mba awat sowat kai wal…®nja vak ng…®l…®nd…®. Ndi kat t…®ga kiyalaa ndi kat kwutaa k…®ta mbaapmamba taagalaa God waa nyaang…®t wutnjangat ndi kat kal…®nd…®.
\v 17 Tamba ngwuk Juda ana ngwuk. Godna ngwaymba ana t…®ngwuk. S…®vlamba t…®ngwuk. Juda ndi Godna ngwaymba t…®ndi. Ngwuk mbaapma v…®l…®l…®lk n…®mba ngwuk aywaa Kraist yalaa ngwuk kat wan apma nyaang…®t yaa mbut…®nd…®. Mbutnd…® maa wutaa ngwuk awat sowat kai wal…®ngwa vak ng…®l…®nd…®.
\v 18 Mbambala Judo nat n…®mbo n…®n aywaa Kraist n…®n kat kwunatnd…®. Kwunatnd…® maa n…®n Godna waagan klan…®n. Nd…®na waagan klalaa God t…®ga kava yalaa k…®tamba ngambugiyan…®n.
\v 19 Ngwuk Juda ana ngwuk. Mbambala Judana n…®m…®ngi vla ana t…®gangwuk. S…®vla ngepmamba l…®ga n…®mba vla ana t…®gangwuk. Ngwutno Judo Godna mbaapma n…®mba k…®tamba t…®gambaapma n…®mba vla t…®gangwuk. Ngwuk Godna nyangu ngwuk.
\v 20 Godna mbaapma ngay vla l…®gand…®. Kraist Jisas ngayna kwaal…®k vla t…®gand…®. Ndi aposel profet ndi waswak vla l…®gandi. Ngwuk mbaw vla l…®gangwuk.
\v 21 Kraist ngay nginja k…®vu vla t…®gand…®. Nd…® ngay kwutaa l…®nd…® maa ngay ana kavle yigiyand…®. Kavle yilapman t…®ga God yet…®giya ngay vla t…®giyand…®.
\v 22 Ngwutno Kraistna mbaapmamba wuleilaa kan ngayna mbaw vla t…®giyangwuk. Nat n…®ma sakwat mbaw vla t…®ga n…®mbonana t…®giyangwuk. Kan ngay Godna waagan yet…®ga ngaya.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Wun Pol wun. Kraist Jisana nj…®vwa kwut…®wun maa wunkat kwutaa kalabusmba taagndi. Nat nj…®vwa kwagalalaa nd…®na nj…®vwa m…®na kwut…®gowun. Ngwuk Juda ana ngwuk. Nat n…®mba ngwuk. Judo Juda ana ndi nat n…®mbo ndi kat God kwutaa nd…®na k…®ta mbaapmamba taaganda vak v…®laa ngwuk kat t…®ga God kat wagala l…®gowun.
\v 2 Ngwuk kat kwunakweya nj…®vwa wan nj…®vwa God wun kat awagapma kwind…®. Kwinda nj…®vwana nyaang…®t tamba wuka t…®gangwuk.
\v 3 God n…®ma sakwat ngepma ngepmamba l…®ga n…®mba kat kwunatndeya vak tak pogwulaa t…®nd…®. God wun kat wan vak tamba pogwulaa t…®nd…®. God wun kat wan vak tamba v…®s…®mogwind…®. Wa v…®s…®mogwinda vak samat tamba lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wutaa ngwuk kat kwigowun.
\v 4 Ngwuk kat kwiwa nyaang…®t v…®ngweyan Kraist wun kat s…®mogwinda vat ngwuk v…®giyangwuk.
\v 5 Tamba la n…®mba God pogwula l…®nda nyaang…®t ndi ana wuka l…®ndi. Mbambala Godna nj…®vwa kwut…®ga aposelogwi profetno ndi wuka l…®gandi. Godna waagan ndi kat v…®s…®mogwind…®.
\v 6 Tak pogwula t…®nda nyaang…®t k…®ngiyand…®. Tamba God Juda kat m…®na apma vat yil…®nd…®. Mbambala ninyangu aywaa wan apma nyaang…®t wutaa Godna mbaapmamba wuleigiyandi. Tamba Juda klanja vla klaigandi Godnanamba. God wand…® maa Kraist Jisas ndinyangu aywaa ndi kat kwunapmak ngaga yand…®. Juda kat m…®na ana yand…®. Wan nyaang…®t tak pogwula t…®nd…®.
\p 
\v 7 Wan apma nyaang…®t yiga mbukweya kwondu God wun kat kwind…®. Apma nyanat t…®wa vak v…®laa ana kwind…®. Kwo kwind…®.
\v 8 Wun Godna n…®mbana njambwi nyan ana wun. Wun mat nyan wun waa yelav…®kwun. Nat n…®mba kat yiga Kraist yigiya n…®ma apma vatna nyaang…®t Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat mbukweya nj…®vwa God wun kat kwo kwind…®. Wan nj…®vwa manda kat wun kat kwo kwind…®. Ana v…®ga t…®gowun. Apma nyan ana wun. Kwinda vak apma vatna. Wan nj…®vwa kwupmat woviyaguga t…®gowun. Apma nj…®vwa.
\v 9 Tak powula t…®nda nyaang…®t ndinyangu kat aywaa yiga mbupmbamb…®n waa God wun kat wand…®. Tak pogwula t…®nda nyaang…®t kak kiyandeya vat ndi kat ambuk waa God wun kat wand…®. Tamba kan k…®pma God kwutnd…®, tamba wan nyaang…®t pogwula t…®nd…®.
\v 10 Mbambala wan nyaang…®t tamba kak kiyand…®. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba wan nyaang…®t wutaa Kraistna mbaapmamba wuleindi. Wuleinja vak v…®laa nyinangwupmba t…®ga njambwi n…®mbagwi enselo waigandi. God apma nambo t…®ga yinda vak vla ndino wupma wuleindi. God yelav…®ka t…®nda vak sakwat vatna. Apma vatna waa waigandi.
\v 11 God n…®n kat wupma ana kwo yind…®. Tamba nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®nda vapma yind…®. God nd…®nai yelav…®kna vapmba wand…® maa n…®na njambwi nyan Kraist Jisas n…®n kat kwunapmak ngaga yand…®.
\v 12 Kraist kat maawupmba yelav…®taa nd…®na mbaapma wuleilaa t…®gan…®n. T…®ga l…®ga God kat ana vaak kiyan…®n. Nd…® kat yalaa ngambugiyan…®n.
\v 13 K…®ta nda ngwuk kat mbuka t…®gowun. Ngwuk kat kwunapmak nj…®vwa kwuka kalil…®wun maa wun kat s…®ga viyal…®gandi. Wun kat viyal…®nja vak kat ngwuk ke yelav…®kngwa. Ngwuk kat kwunatuwa njivwa njgwulo ngwuk kat kwunakiyand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga solat as…® ngwula.
\s1 KRAIST N∆óN KAT YELAV∆óKA L∆óNDA VAK V∆óNJANGAT WAND∆ó POL
\p 
\v 14 N…®na nyaek God wan nj…®vwa wun kat kwind…® maa kwali kwali s…®laa nd…® kat s…®vu l…®l…®gowun.
\v 15 God n…®na nyaekna. K…®pmo nyinangwutno mbaapma mbaapma t…®ga n…®mbana nyaekna.
\v 16 Godnana apma vat n…®ma sakwat t…®gand…®. God wand…® maa nd…®na waagan ngwuk kat kwondu kwindangat wowun. Kwind…® maa klalaa njwula maawut tagula maawut t…®giyand…®.
\v 17 Kraist kat ngwula maawupmba yelav…®kngwangat wowun. Kraist ngwuk kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®nda vak kat yelav…®kngweyan ngwut n…®ma njingwut t…®ga mi vla t…®giyangwuk. Ana kavle yigiyangwuk.
\v 18 Ngwutno Godna mbaapmamba l…®ga aywaa t…®ga n…®mbo Kraist n…®n kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®nda vak ngwulo v…®ngwangat wowun. Samat v…®ngwangat ana wowun. Aywaa v…®ngwangat wowun.
\v 19 Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga wan vak aywaa ana v…®ga t…®giyangwuk. Nyinangwut wokengweyan aywaa v…®ga t…®giyangwuk. Godnana vak ngwutna maawupmba n…®ma sakwat t…®ndangat wowun.
\p 
\v 20 God kat wagalaneya vak kat kwulaka apma vat yil…®gand…® n…®n kat. nd…®namba klavat yelav…®tneya vak kat kwulaka apma vat yil…®gand…® n…®n kat. N…®n kat nd…®na kwondu kwind…® maa apma vat t…®gan…®n.
\v 21 God nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat apma vat yind…®. Apma vat yinda vak v…®laa nat n…®mba waigandi. God apma nyana waa waigandi. God wand…® maa Kraist Jisas apma nj…®vwa kwutnda vak v…®laa waigan…®n. God apma nyanat t…®nda vat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®giyand…®. Ana nd…® ng…®l…®giyand…® waa waigan…®n.
\c 4
\s1 N∆óN KRAISTNA MBANG∆ó VLA T∆óGAN∆óN
\p 
\v 1 Wun njambwi nyana nj…®vwa kwut…®wun maa v…®laa wun kat kwutaa kalabusmba taagandi, t…®gowun. God ngwuk kat nd…®na mbaapmba taaganda nj…®mbla ngwuk kat wupma yet…® ngwula waa wanda nyaang…®pmba yet…® ngwula. Ke kwagalaga.
\v 2 Wun njambwi nyan wun waa ke wangwa. Nat n…®mba kat n…®mamba kwondu wogwuga ke t…®ngwa. Nat n…®mba kat kawiga al…® ngwula. Nat n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®kngweyan ndi kat kwkunak ngwula. Kwunat…®ngwa vak v…®laa n…®n kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®gandi waa waigandi.
\v 3 Godna waagan k…®ta vat yet…®ngwangat ngwuk kat wal…®gand…®. Wan wal…®nda vak ke kwagalangwa. Ngwuk kat kwinda apma maawut ngwuk kat k…®ta mbaapmamba nginja yaaw vla t…®gand…®.
\v 4 Godna mbaapma k…®ta mbaapmat. Godna waagan k…®ta m…®na t…®gand…®. God n…®n kat yagwa walaa ng…®ni n…®n kat kwunatndeya vak kat kawiga l…®gan…®n. Kawiga t…®na vat k…®ta vakna.
\v 5 N…®na njambwi nyan k…®ta nyana. Maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®na nyan k…®ta nyana. Ngu yagulaa nd…®na mbaapma wuleina vat k…®ta vatna.
\v 6 God nd…® k…®ta t…®gand…®. Ndinyangu aywaa ndina nyaekna. Ndinyangu aywaa ndina njambwi nyana. N…®no aywaa nd…®na kwundi wuka yet…®l…®gan…®n. N…®no aywaa n…®na maawupmba yet…®l…®gand…® God.
\p 
\v 7 Kraist n…®n kat k…®ta nyan k…®ta nyan kwutneya nj…®vwana kwondu n…®n kat kwind…®.
\v 8 Tamba la n…®mba God waa nyaang…®t lavu ningamba kupma p…®l…®wutndi.
\li1 Y…®ga n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat kandi kwutaa kaliga
