\li1 kwind…®
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi.
\v 9 Nyinangwut wokend…® waa manda kat p…®l…®wutndi. Anda kaamba t…®ga wokend…®. Tak ndaind…®. k…®pma pulat ndailaa wokend…®.
\v 10 K…®pma pulat ndailaa nyinangwutnat wokend…®. Wokelaa kava kava aywaa wun v…®ga l…®gowun wand…®.
\v 11 ‚ÄúNdi kat n…®ma wenga kwind…®‚Äù waa tamba lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wutndi. Ndi kat kwutnjeya nj…®vwana kwondu kwind…®. Nat n…®mba kat aposelna nj…®vwa kwind…®. Nat n…®mba kat profetna nj…®vwa kwind…®. Nat n…®mba kat ngwuk kava kava yiga wuna nyaang…®t mbuka evanselisna nj…®vwa akwuk ngwula waa wand…®. Nat n…®mba kat ngwuk wuna mbaapma n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®ga pastona nj…®vwa akwuk ngwula wan wand…®. Nat n…®mba kat tisana nj…®vwa kwind…®.
\v 12 Nat n…®mba Godna nj…®vwa apma vat kwutnjangat ndi kat mand…®p mand…®p nj…®vwa kwind…®. Wan nj…®vwa kwuka Kraistna mbaapma n…®mba awat sowat ndino kwunak kiyandi.
\v 13-14 Kwunatndi maa k…®ta vak yelav…®ka Godna nyana angwa vak yelav…®ka v…®ga l…®giyan…®n. Nd…®na nagwa vak v…®laa mat nyangu vla ana t…®giyan…®n. N…®no n…®ma nyangu vla l…®giyan…®n. Kraist t…®nda vla t…®giyan…®n. Kraist t…®nda vla t…®ga woseka waiga n…®mbana kwundi ana wuka t…®giyan…®n. Nat n…®mbana maawut kavle yivak kat ngambunjeyan ana wuk kiyan…®n. tagula maawutno t…®giyan…®n. Mwuk pali viyand…®, yi ya l…®ga vaala vla n…®na maawut ana wupma t…®giyand…®.
\v 15 Wan kavle vat ana yigiyan…®n. N…®n nat n…®mba kat ana woseka waigan…®n. Ndi kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka apma nyaang…®pmba ngambu kiyan…®n. Yet…®neya vak aywaa Kraist yeta vla yet…®giyan…®n. Nd…® n…®na njambwi nyana.
\v 16 N…®n katkwinda mand…®p mand…®p nj…®vwa kwuka nd…®na mbang…®na nda vla l…®giyan…®n. nd…®nai yelav…®k vapmba mand…®p mand…®p nj…®vwa kwut…®gan…®n. K…®ita nyana mbang…®na nda kavle yind…®, nd…®na mbang…®na nat nda kwunakiyand…®. N…®no wupma t…®gan…®n. Mand…®p mand…®p nj…®vwa kwuka awat sowat kwunat…®gan…®n.
\s1 MAND∆óP VAPMBA YET∆ó NGWULA
\p 
\v 17 Njambwi nyan waa vak ngwuk kat wowun. Awuk ngwula. Godna nyaang…®t wutapman n…®mba yet…®nja vla ke yet…®ngwa. Ndi kavle savle maawut yelav…®ka yet…®gandi.
\v 18 Ndina maawut kulun wala t…®ga nda vla t…®gand…®. God kwiya apma maawut ana klal…®ndi. Ndi klavak kat kai waa kavle savle yelav…®ka t…®gandi.
\v 19 Ndina mbang…® wup ana yil…®gand…®. Apma vat kwagalalaa kavle vat m…®na yiga yet…®gandi. Mand…®p mand…®p kavle vak yiga yet…®gandi.
\p 
\v 20 Yiga yet…®nja vak Kraistnanamba wukngwa nyaang…®t kapma nyaang…®tna.
\v 21 Kraistna nyaang…®t tamba wuka yet…®gangwuk. Wutaa nd…®na mbaapma wuleingwuk maa nat n…®mba Jisasna angwa vak ngwuk kat v…®s…®mogwindi.
\v 22 Ngwutna tamba maawut kwagala ngwula. Tamba wungi kavle maawupmba yet…®ngwuk. Kwagala ngwula. Tamba yiga yet…®ngwa kavle vat ngwula maawuk kat kavle yil…®nd…®.
\v 23 Mbambala kupi maawupmba yelav…®ka yet…® ngwula.
\v 24 Kan wawa kupi maawut Godnana maawut t…®ga vla t…®gand…®. Kan kupi maawupmba yelav…®kngweyan apma nj…®vwa m…®na kwuka apma vat yelav…®ka yet…®giyangwuk.
\p 
\v 25 Tamba woseka waa yet…®ngwa vak kwagala ngwula. Ngwuk k…®ta mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk. Ngwuk awat sowat ke woseka wangwa.
\v 26 Nat nyan kat nj…®kngweyan wan nj…®kngweya vat ke wata l…®nda. T…®ga yiga ngan ndandeyan kavle vat yigiyangwuk. Kwiyatapman kwagala ngwula. Kavle vatna.
\v 27 Seten kat nj…®ka wangwuk, yigand…®. Nj…®ka walapman yingweyan ngwula maawuk kat kavle yigiyand…®.
\v 28 Tamba lamba nat n…®mbana nda s…®kwut…®ga n…®mba wan vak kwagala ngwula. Wan vak kwagalalaa nj…®vwa kwutaa wenga klalaa sanya lapman n…®mba kat agwi ngwula.
\v 29 Nat nyan kat ke s…®mbwiga wangwa. Nd…® kat kwunakngweya vat m…®na ngambu ngwula. Wupma ngambungweyan wutqa n…®mba apma maawut yelav…®ka apma vat yet…®giyandi. Ndi kat kwunakiyangwuk.
\v 30 K…®ta kavle nda ke ngambungwa. Godna waagana maawut ngwuk kat mbaak kavle yiland…®. Godna waagana maawut ngwuk kat mbaak kavle yiland…®. Nd…® Godna waagan ngwuk kat apma maawut kwil…®gand…®. Kwinda maawupmba yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni God n…®n kat apma vat aywaa kwunak kiyand…® waa yelav…®t…®gangwuk.
\v 31 Kavle n…®mba ndi waa ngwula maawupmba ke yelav…®kngwa. Ngwula mbang…® waiga vak ke wukngwa. Nat n…®mba kat ke woku walea t…®ngwa. Nat n…®mba kat ke kai wangwa.
\v 32 Wan kavle vat kwagalalaa nat n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka apma vat ndi kat ay ngwula. God kat kavle vat yingwa vak tamba kwagaland…®. Kraist s…®l…®mbwind…® maa kwagaland…®. Ana ng…®ni yelav…®ka t…®gand…® wan vak. Ngwuk kat nat n…®mba kavle vat yinja vak ngwutno kwagala ngwula. Ng…®ni ke yelav…®ka t…®ngwa.
\c 5
\s1 APMA VAT YIGA YET∆ó NGWULA
\p 
\v 1 Ngwuk Godna n…®mba ngwuk. Ngwuk kat woviyaguga t…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga yet…®nda vla yet…® ngwula.
\v 2 Kraist n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®ga n…®n kat t…®ga kiyand…®. Kiyanda vat tamba la Juda God kat kwunapmak kwinja nda vla t…®gand…®. Tamba Juda God kat kwinja ndana njangu wutaa l…®ga wand…®. Apma vatna wun kat yingwa waa God wand…®. Kraist n…®n kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®nda vla n…®no nat n…®mba kat wupma n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®giyan…®n.
\p 
\v 3 S…®k yamb…®s…®k yiga kavle vat yiga nat n…®mbana nda klavat wal…®nja vak ke yingw
\v 4 Kavle kwundi, nat n…®mba kat kwus…®s…®l…®gan ngambul…®nja kwundi, nj…®ka wal…®nja kwundi ngwuk ke wangwa. God kat m…®na apma kwundi ngambuga nd…® kat s…®vu k…®ga al…® ngwula.
\v 5 K…®ta nda v…®ngwangat wowun. S…®k yamb…®s…®k yil…®ga n…®mba kavle vat yil…®ga n…®mba, nat nyana nda klavat wal…®ga n…®mba Godno Kraist …®ga l…®ga kava ana wuleigiyandi. Nd…® k…®ta nyan nat n…®mbana nda klavat yelav…®ka t…®ndeyan kavle waagan kwunat…®giya nyan vla t…®giyand…®.
\p 
\v 6 Wan kavle vat yingweyan God ngwuk kat ana s…®giyand…® waa wal…®ga n…®mbana nyaang…®t ke wukngwa. Ngwuk kat woseka wal…®gandi. Nd…®na nyaang…®t wupmak kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba nd…®na nyingi maawupmba t…®ga ndi kat s…®giyand…®.
\v 7 K…®ndi n…®mba kavle nyaang…®t woseka waa yet…®ga n…®mba ndi. Ndinogwinana ke yet…®ngwa.
\v 8 Ngwuk tamba kulun wala la kava ta n…®mba vla t…®ngwuk. Mbambala tamba njambwi nyana n…®mba t…®gangwuk. Ngwuk kemba l…®ga kava t…®ga n…®mba vla t…®gangwuk. Kembaga l…®ga kava t…®ga n…®mba apma vapmba yet…®gandi. Ngwulo wupma apma vat yet…® ngwula.
\v 9 Kemba kavamba t…®ga vla apma vat yet…®ga n…®mba ndi kavle vat kwagalalaa apma vat m…®na yet…®ga woseka ana wal…®gandi.
\v 10 Njambwi nyan woviyaguga t…®nda vak kat kwaka al…® ngwula.
\v 11 Kulun wala l…®ga kavamba t…®ga kavle vat yet…®ga n…®mbanala ke l…®ngwa. Yil…®nja kavle vat kwo vatna. Ndi kat wan apma vat v…®s…®mogwi ngwula.
\v 12 Pogwuga yil…®nja kavle vat kat wun ana mbuk kiyowun. Mbupmak kat wuna mbang…® wup yigand…®.
\v 13 Pogwula kavle vapmba yet…®ga n…®mba apma vat yiga yet…®neya vak kat v…®laa yelav…®kiyandi. N…®n kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®gan…®n waa yelav…®kiyandi.
\v 14 N…®n kavle vak yiga yet…®l…®gan…®n waa yelav…®taa kavle vak kwagalalaa apma vak yet…®giyandi. Tamba la nyan lavu nyingamba nd…®no wupma p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\li1 S…®ndukwal…®ga nyan laap m…®la. Kiya nyano laap
\li1 m…®la. Laapm…®n maa Kraist yalaa apma vat m…®n kat
\li1 s…®mogwi kiyand…®.
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\p 
\v 15 Ngwuk s…®mblan ke yet…®ngwa. Apma maawut yelav…®ka yet…® ngwula. Maawut yelav…®tapman yet…®ga n…®mba vla ke yet…®ngwa.
\v 16 Kan mbambala t…®na nj…®mbla n…®ma sakwat kavle vat t…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka apma vapmba yet…® ngwula. Ke kwo yet…®ngwa.
\v 17 Ngwuk s…®mblan ke yet…®ngwa. Njambwi nyan woviyaguga t…®nda vak v…®laa wungi vapmba yet…® ngwula.
\p 
\v 18 N…®ma ngu n…®ma sakwat ke k…®ngwa. N…®ma sakwat k…®ngweyan tungwengwan yiga kavle yigiyangwuk. Godna waagan ngwukkat n…®mamba wuleiga ngwula mbang…® tavindeyan wovuna. Apma vatna.
\v 19 Godna s…® katsovat vi mbangu veiga Godna nyaang…®t t…®ga mbangu kwundi nglas…® kwundi, wama kwundi awat sowat waga al…® ngwula. Wan apma vatna. God kat nd…® kat wama kwundi nglas…® kwundi nd…® kat katsovat ngambu ngwula.
\v 20 N…®na nyaek God n…®n kat yinda nda kat yelav…®taa nd…® kat s…®vu ag…® ngwula. N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistna s…® waga nd…® kat s…®vu ag…® ngwula.
\s1 NDU TAAGWANA NYANG∆óT
\p 
\v 21 Kraist n…®na njambwi nyana. N…®n mat nyangu vla l…®gan…®n walaa nat n…®mbana nyaang…®t awuk ngwula.
\v 22 Njambwi nyana kwundi wut…®na vak vla ngwut taagwa ngwutno ngwula lana kwundi awuk ngwula.
\v 23 Kraist nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbana njambwi nyanat t…®nda vla nd…®no wupma ndu nd…®na taagwana njambwi nyanat t…®gand…®. Kraist nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat kwunatnd…® maa nd…®na mbang…® vla t…®gandi.
\v 24 N…®n Kraistna mbaapma n…®mba nd…®na kwundi wut…®na vla ngwulo taagwa wupma ngwula lana kwundi awuk ngwula.
\p 
\v 25 Kraist nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®ga ndi kat t…®ga kiyand…®. Ndi kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka t…®nda vla ngwukndungwutna taagwakat wupma yelav…®ka al…® ngwula.
\v 26 Nd…® Kraist nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat t…®ga kiyand…® maa nd…®na nyaang…®t wutaa ngu yagundi. Ngu yagundi, ndina kavle vak ng…®l…®nd…®. Ng…®l…®nd…® maa Kraist ndi kat kwutaa wenga nda vla God kat kwind…®.
\v 27 Kraist nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kwunataa ndu taagwa kat klanja vla Kraist wupma ndi kat kland…®. Ndi kat Kraist kwunatnd…® maa ndi apma vat m…®na t…®gandi. Ndi yigin taagwa vla t…®gandi. Mbang…® k…®s…® tapman nglambi tapman t…®ga nyangu vla t…®gandi. Apma vat m…®na t…®gandi.
\v 28 Ngwut ndu avla ngwula mbang…® kwunakngweya vak vla ngwutna taagwana mbang…® wupma kwunak ngwula. Ngwut k…®ta mbang…® nda vla t…®gangwuk.
\v 29 Nat nyan ana nd…®na mbang…® avla kavle yil…®gand…®. Nd…®na mbang…® kwunaka k…®g…®nda kwil…®gand…®. Kraist wupma nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat kwunat…®gand…®.
\v 30 Nd…® nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba n…®n.
\v 31 Nd…® tamba la nyan God waa nyaang…®t wutaa nd…® lavu nyingamba tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\li1 God wand…® maa k…®ta nyan nd…®na nyaek nyime
\li1 kwagalalaa nd…®na taagwonana yet…®giyand…®. Mb…®k
\li1 ng…®ni k…®ta nda vla t…®giyamb…®k
\p waa tamba lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\v 32 Wan p…®l…®wuta nyaang…®tna angwa vak ngil…®ga. Kraist nd…®na mbapma n…®mba k…®tamba yet…®nja vak kat yelav…®taa lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\v 33 Wan p…®l…®wuta nyaang…®tna angwa vat nat k…®ta ligand…®. Ndu taagwakat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Mat nyangu ngwutna nyaek nyimena nyaang…®t awuk ngwula. Njambwi nyan wupma yingwangat ngwuk kat wand…®. Ndina nyaang…®t wukngweyan apma vatna.
\v 2 God tambakwiya njambiyana k…®ta njambiya kwupma lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wutndi.
\p Nyaek nyimena nyaang…®t kwuka ndi kat kwunak ngwula waa lavu nyingamba p…®l…®wutndi. Nat njambiya kwo p…®l…®wutndi. Kan njambiya apma nyaang…®tno k…®tamba p…®l…®wutndi.
\p 
\v 3 Nyaek nyimena kwundi wuka t…®ngweyan apma vat t…®ga ka k…®pmamba n…®ma nj…®mbla t…®giyaangwuk. Waa p…®l…®wutndi.
\p 
\v 4 Nyaek nyime ngwutna nyangu kat n…®ma vat kwo ke yingwa. N…®ma vat kwo yingweyan ngwuk kat awat walea t…®giyandi. Njambwi nyan waa nyaang…®pmba ndi kat kwunak ngwula.
\p 
\v 5 Nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba ngwutna v…®ga la n…®mbana nyaang…®t awuk ngwula. Ndi kat kai waa ke wangwa. Maawut v…®l…®l…®k v…®l…®l…®k yelav…®ka nj…®vwa ke kwukngwa. Kraistna nj…®vwa kwukngwqa vla ndina nj…®vwa agwuk ngwula.
\v 6 Nj…®vwa v…®ga l…®ga nyan ngwuk kat v…®ga la nj…®mbla m…®na ke wanda nj…®vwa kwukngwa. Njwmbla nj…®mbla wanda nj…®vwa agwuk ngwula. Ngwuk kat v…®lapman yinda nj…®mbla n…®mbun wanda nj…®vwa agwuk ngwula. N…®mamba ngwutna nj…®vwa kwukngwangat God ngwuk kat wand…®. Kraistna nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba vla t…®gangwuk.
\v 7 Kwut…®ngwa nj…®vwa kat ke nj…®ka waga. Ngwuk kwo solat s…®ga nj…®vwa kwuka t…®giyangwuk. Njambwi nyan Polna nj…®vwa kwut…®gowun waa yelav…®taa nat nyana nj…®vwa nd…®no agwuk ngwula.
\v 8 Sanya klavat nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mbo apma vat nj…®vwa kwutnjeyan God ndi kat apma wenga kwigiyand…®.
\p 
\v 9 Ngwuk nj…®vwa v…®ga l…®ga n…®mba ngwutna nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba kat apma vat ay ngwula. Ngwuk kat apma vat yinja vla ndi kat wupma apma vat ay ngwula. n…®maba ndi kat wupma apma vat ay ngwula. N…®maba ndi kat mugu njaw viya ke waa. Yigamba ndi kat wangwuk vaatapman t…®ga n…®jvwa kwukandi. K…®ta vak kat yelav…®k ngwula. Ngwutno ngwutna nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mbo ngwut aywaa ngwutna njambwi nyan God k…®ta l…®gand…® nyinangwupmba. Njambwi nyanat t…®na vat v…®laa n…®n kat ana yil…®gand…®. God n…®n kat aywaa k…®ta vat m…®na yil…®gand…®.
\v 10 Ng…®nina nyaang…®tna p…®l…®wupmat yuwa. njambwi nyanonana yet…®ga nd…®nai kwiya ava agla ngwula.
\v 11 God kwiya kao n…®mba kwusoa waavwi ngwutno kwuso ngwula. kwusolaa Seten ngwuk kat kavle vat yindeya vak kat kwulak kiyangwuk. Ngwuk kat ana s…®giyand…®.
\v 12 Nat n…®mba kat kao yil…®ga n…®mba vla ana t…®gan…®n. N…®n nyinangwupmba l…®ga kavle n…®mba kat kao yiga l…®gan…®n. N…®n kavle waagan kavle wundumbu kavle wunjumbu kat kao yiga t…®gan…®n. Wundi kavle nda Setena kwundi wuka nd…®na nj…®vwa kwut…®gandi.
\v 13 God kwiya kao n…®mba kwuso waavwi mbambala ngwuk kwuso ngwula. Wan waavwi kwusongweyan kao yiga t…®ga n…®mba ngwuk kat ana s…®ga viyaigandi.
\p 
\v 14 Kao yavat yigand…®. V…®ga al…® ngwula. God waa apma nyaang…®t yipmamba s…®kngwa let vla t…®giyand…®. God apma vat yiga yet…®nda vak mawlava kapmongwa siot kapa vla t…®giyand…®.
\v 15 Nat n…®mba kat wan apma nyaang…®t mbutnja vak kwusolaa l…®ngwa su vla t…®gand…®.
\v 16 God kat yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®nja vak ngwula waag…®t vla t…®giyand…®. Kan waag…®t kwukngweyan Seten ngwuk kat yaagigiya ya v…®t…®ga vi ngwuk kat ana s…®giyand…®.
\v 17 God n…®n kat kwunatnda vak kumbula l…®ngwa kapa hat vla l…®giyand…®. Godna waagan Godna nyaang…®t ngwuk kat mbut…®ga vak waleavat kwutaa yingwa yak vla t…®giyand…®. Wan walea nda Godnanamba klalaa kavle vak kat waleagiyangwuk.
\v 18 Ngwuk kwo kavle vak kat ana kao yigiyangwuk. God kat wagalangwuk, ngwuk kat kwondu kwind…® maa m…®na kao yigiyangwuk. Godna waagan God kat wagala ngwula waa wand…® maa ngwuk wagala ngwula. Godna n…®mba kat t…®ga God kat wagala ngwula. Kavle vak kat kao yil…®ngwa vak ke kwagalangwa. Kao yivak kat ngwula mbang…® ke k…®l…®p mbang…® yinda.
\v 19 Wuno wun kat t…®ga God kat wagala ngwula. Mbukweya nj…®mbla mbukweya nyaang…®t wun kat s…®mogwimband…® walaa wunkat wagala ngwula. Tamba pogwula yet…®nda apma nyaang…®t mbambala kapmba mbukwangat wagala ngwula.
\v 20 Wuna nj…®vwa k…®ngiyan. Wun kapmba wan apma nyaang…®t yi ya mbut…®gowun. mbambala ana yi ya yet…®l…®gowun. Kalabusmba yet…®l…®gowun. Wan apma nyaang…®t n…®ma kwundimba kapmba ngambuweyan wovuna. Apma vatna. Wupma mbukwangat wagala ngwula.
\v 21 Wowun maa k…®ta nyan yetuwa v…®laa ngwuk kat yiga mbuk kiyand…®. Nd…®na s…® Tikikas. Nd…® n…®na k…®ta mbaapma nyana. Nd…® apma nyana waa wal…®gan…®n.
\v 22 Yet…®l…®na vat ngwuk kat yiga mbutndangat wowun. Wowun maa yigiyand…®. Ngwutna ngepma yalaa ngwutna maawut kwunak kiyand…®.
\p 
\v 23 N…®na nyaek God n…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistno ngwuk kat apma maawut kwimbangat wowun. God kat yelav…®ka l…®ga n…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®ngwa vat ngwuk kat kwimbangat wowun.
\v 24 N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla woviyaguga t…®ga n…®mba God awagapma kwil…®nda apma nda klambandi walaa wowun. a kat klanja vla Kraist wupma ndi kat kland…®. Ndi kat Kraist kwunatnd…® maa ndi apma vat m…®na t…®gandi 
